OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772071403
OL,3,CMore than 800,000 UK homes could be at
OL,4,Chigh risk of flooding by 2080
OL,6,FMore than 800,000 homes could be at
OL,7,Fhigh risk of severe flooding by 2080,
OL,8,Fan analysis has found, as green groups
OL,9,Fwarn of the growing impacts of climate
OL,10,Fchange on UK households.
OL,12,FCampaigners are urging the government
OL,13,Fand other parties to make polluters
OL,14,Fpay, increase funding for local
OL,15,Fauthorities and emergency services,
OL,16,Fand ensure access to affordable home
OL,17,Finsurance ahead of the local elections.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
