OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772071403
OL,3,CMore than 800,000 UK homes could be at
OL,4,Chigh risk of flooding by 2080
OL,6,FCommunities across the UK have been
OL,7,Fhit by storms, persistent rainfall and
OL,8,Fflooding in recent weeks, with the
OL,9,FSouth East and south of England
OL,10,Frecording their wettest start to a
OL,11,Fyear on record.
OL,13,FAbout 866,000 homes could face a
OL,14,F"high" or "very high" risk of flooding
OL,15,Fby 2080 if global temperatures rise by
OL,16,F2.4C above pre-industrial levels,
OL,17,Faccording to research by flood risk
OL,18,Fassessment firm Geosmart for
OL,19,FGreenpeace.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@FO]vD@KOUvD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772071403
OL,3,CMore than 800,000 UK homes could be at
OL,4,Chigh risk of flooding by 2080
OL,6,FThe analysis compared flood risk
OL,7,Facross regions and local authorities
OL,8,Fin Britain under that climate
OL,9,Fscenario. It found that 386,716 homes
OL,10,Fin Scotland ` 19% of the country's
OL,11,Fhousing stock ` could be at high or
OL,12,Fvery high risk.
OL,14,FSouth East England could see 122,484
OL,15,Fhomes affected (2% of the region's
OL,16,Ftotal), followed by 71,431 in Wales
OL,17,F(5%), 65,884 in the South West (3%)
OL,18,Fand 59,918 in the East of England (2%).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772071403
OL,3,CMore than 800,000 UK homes could be at
OL,4,Chigh risk of flooding by 2080
OL,6,FElsewhere, 53,229 homes in the East
OL,7,FMidlands (2%) could face that level of
OL,8,Frisk, along with 45,320 in the North
OL,9,FWest (2%), 35,459 in Yorkshire and the
OL,10,FHumber (2%), 18,049 in the West
OL,11,FMidlands (1%) and 7,595 in the North
OL,12,FEast (1%).
OL,14,FPhillip Evans, Greenpeace UK's senior
OL,15,Fclimate campaigner, said: "The
OL,16,Feconomic cost of the storms and floods
OL,17,Fbattering Britain is skyrocketing.
OL,19,F"Our data clearly shows that more and
OL,20,Fmore homes will face rising flood risk
OL,21,Fdue to extreme weather events.
OL,26,@wD@[OU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
