SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772071403
OL,3,CMore than 800,000 UK homes could be at
OL,4,Chigh risk of flooding by 2080
OL,6,F"Already, homes in some areas are
OL,7,Fbecoming uninsurable and in certain
OL,8,Fcases insurers are abandoning towns,
OL,9,Fleaving councils to pick up the tab."
OL,11,FThe Intergovernmental Panel on Climate
OL,12,FChange estimates global temperatures
OL,13,Fcould rise by around 2.7C by 2100
OL,14,Funder current government policies,
OL,15,Fwith a 2.4C increase by 2080 fitting
OL,16,Fwith that mid-range scenario.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
