OL,3,CMore than 800,000 UK homes could be at
OL,4,Chigh risk of flooding by 2080
OL,6,FIn the UK, scientists say weather
OL,7,Fpatterns have grown increasingly
OL,8,Fvolatile, with six of the ten wettest
OL,9,Fwinters on record occurring in the
OL,10,Fpast 20 years.
OL,12,FSeparate analysis of Environment
OL,13,FAgency data by Friends of the Earth,
OL,14,Fpublished on Wednesday, found that one
OL,15,Fmillion homes in England ` home to
OL,16,Fabout 2.4 million people ` are already
OL,17,Fat the highest risk of flooding.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
