OL,3,CMore than 800,000 UK homes could be at
OL,4,Chigh risk of flooding by 2080
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIf countries fail to reduce greenhouse
OL,12,Fgas emissions, a further 1.89 million
OL,13,Fpeople could be pushed into the
OL,14,Fhighest risk category, the research
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
