OL,3,CMore than 800,000 UK homes could be at
OL,4,Chigh risk of flooding by 2080
OL,6,FThe study also highlighted wider
OL,7,Fsocial vulnerabilities, identifying
OL,8,F611,000 people who are least able to
OL,9,Fprepare for, respond to or recover
OL,10,Ffrom flooding due to factors such as
OL,11,Flow incomes, renting, disability or a
OL,12,Flack of insurance.
OL,14,FA government spokesperson said: "This
OL,15,Fgovernment takes the threat of
OL,16,Fflooding extremely seriously, pumping
OL,17,Fadditional money into repairing and
OL,18,Fmaintaining our defences.
OL,26,@vD@aOU
