OL,3,CMore than 800,000 UK homes could be at
OL,4,Chigh risk of flooding by 2080
OL,6,F"This is alongside investing a record
OL,7,F#10.5 billion investment to better
OL,8,Fprotect nearly 900,000 properties by
OL,9,F2036.
OL,11,F"We will continue to work closely with
OL,12,FFlood Re and industry so that people
OL,13,Fcan access affordable insurance as we
OL,14,Fbuild 1.5 million new homes, with our
OL,15,Fnew planning proposals ensuring
OL,16,Fdevelopment should not go ahead where
OL,17,Fit would be unsafe due to flood risk."
